title: Daruna | Petani
description: Eratani selalu memberikan dukungan untuk petani perempuan. Maju terus Eratani!
description_eng: Eratani always gives full support to us female farmers. Keep moving forward, Eratani!

title: Tarjaya | Petani
description: Eratani itu berkah bagi saya. Banyak kekurangan petani yang dibantu Eratani. Saya jadi lebih semangat untuk bertani.
description_eng: Eratani is a blessing for me. There are many farmers’ shortcomings that are helped by Eratani. So, I am more enthusiastic to farm.

title: Danawi | Petani
description: Dengan adanya Eratani, para petani dipermudah dari permodalan dan pengetahuan. Eratani #SelaluAdaUntukPetani
description_eng: With Eratani, farmers are facilitated with funding and knowledge. Eratani #SelaluAdaUntukPetani

title: Warsoni | Petani
description: Harapan saya Eratani semakin meluas karena petani sangat amat dibantu dengan adanya Eratani. Terimakasih Eratani!
description_eng: I hope Eratani will get bigger because farmers are greatly helped by the existence of Eratani. Thank you Eratani!
